snippet.title: What could possibly be more entertaining and funny than animals - Super funny animal compilation
snippet.description:
Do you want to laugh, do you need something to cheer you up?What's better than funny pets and animals? :D In this compilation you can see so many funny and cute cats, dogs, squirrels, crabs, parrots..., making funny sounds and noises, playing, getting their heads stuck in boxes, playing with leafblowers, failing and so on! What is your favourite clip? ;) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!

WANT TO SEE YOUR PET IN OUR COMPILATIONS?
Send your clips or links to: tigerlicensing@gmail.com

For more funny videos & pictures visit and like our Facebook page:
https://www.facebook.com/tigerstudiosfun
